gitosis: gitosis (software for hosting git repositories)
gitosis:
gitosis: Manage git repositories, provide access to them over SSH,
gitosis: with tight access control and not needing shell accounts.
gitosis:
gitosis: gitosis aims to make hosting git repos easier and safer. It
gitosis: manages multiple repositories under one user account, using SSH keys
gitosis: to identify users. End users do not need shell accounts on the server,
gitosis: they will talk to one shared account that will not let them run
gitosis: arbitrary commands.
gitosis:
